"Software" means the SOA Gateway for Autonomous Safety-Supervisor source code,
header files, build scripts, documentation, and associated materials contained
in this repository, collectively constituting a reference implementation of a
SOME/IP & DDS integration middleware for the NXP S32G System-on-Chip.

"You" (or "Your") means the individual or legal entity exercising permissions
granted by this License.

"Commercial Use" means any use of the Software, in whole or in part, directly
or indirectly, for the purpose of generating revenue, including but not limited
to integration into a commercial product, use in a commercial service offering,
or use to support commercial consulting engagements.

